V0303_01_00_00_0.text:
Of course I miss him.
Things ended so suddenly between us.

V0303_01_00_00_1.text: I wish I had another chance to tell him what he meant to me.

V0303_01_00_01_0.text: A Duelist never turns down a Duel!

V0303_01_00_05_0.text:
Kaiba, listen to me.
He's... gone.

V0303_01_00_06_0.text: Kaiba, I'm now ready to fight on my own!

V0303_01_00_11_0.text:
Aigami, I don't know who you are...
But I will defeat you!

V0303_01_00_12_0.text: I'll always fight for a friend!

V0303_05_00_00_0.text: I still believe in the heart of the cards!

V0303_06_01_01_0.text: That's what I was waiting for!

V0303_07_09_01_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0303_08_00_00_0.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Mystical Space Typhoon!

V0303_08_00_02_0.text: By giving you a card, I can activate Magical Contract Door!

V0303_08_00_02_1.text: It lets me acquire a new monster!

V0303_08_00_03_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Silent Burning!

V0303_08_00_03_1.text: We both draw until we have six cards in our hands!

V0303_08_00_04_0.text: I banish Silent Burning to get Silent Magician from my deck!

V0303_08_00_05_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Silent Sword Slash!

V0303_08_00_06_0.text: I banish Silent Sword Slash to acquire Silent Swordsman!

V0303_08_00_08_0.text: The Continuous Spell, Dark Magical Circle!

V0303_08_00_09_0.text: Dark Magical Circle banishes one of your cards!

V0303_08_00_10_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Dark Magic Inheritance!

V0303_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Bond Between Teacher and Student!

V0303_08_00_12_0.text: Dark Magician will inherit Dark Magician Girl's strength!

V0303_08_00_12_1.text: The Spell Card, Dark Magic Twin Burst!

V0303_08_00_13_0.text: Dark Magician Girl will destroy your monsters!

V0303_08_00_13_1.text: The Spell Card, Dark Burning Attack!

V0303_08_00_14_0.text: My Magicians will work together to destroy all your cards!

V0303_08_00_14_1.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Dark Burning Magic!

V0303_08_00_15_0.text: Dark Magician will destroy all your Spells and Traps!

V0303_08_00_15_1.text: The Spell Card, Dark Magic Attack!

V0303_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Dark Magic Expanded!

V0303_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Ritual Spell!
Chaos Form!

V0303_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Dark Horizon!

V0303_08_00_18_1.text: Since I took damage, I can Special Summon this monster!

V0303_08_00_20_1.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Dimension Sphinx!

V0303_08_00_21_0.text: When your monster has more ATK than mine, you take damage!

V0303_08_00_23_0.text: You failed to destroy my monster, so you gotta attack again!

V0303_08_00_24_0.text:
Final Geas!
Banish all monsters from our Graveyards!

V0303_08_00_25_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Magicians' Defense!

V0303_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Dig of Destiny!

V0303_08_00_27_1.text: Since I took damage, I draw a card!

V0303_08_00_28_0.text: Dig of Destiny's effect lets me draw cards!

V0303_08_00_29_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Spiritual Swords of Revealing Light!

V0303_08_00_30_0.text: Spiritual Swords of Revealing Light negates your attack!

V0303_08_00_30_1.text: But I must pay 1000 LP in exchange!

V0303_08_00_31_0.text: By banishing Spiritual Swords, you can't attack me directly!

V0303_08_00_32_0.text: I activate my Trap, Mirror Force!

V0303_08_00_33_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Magic Cylinder!

V0303_08_00_34_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Eternal Soul!

V0303_08_00_36_0.text: When Eternal Soul is destroyed, so are all my monsters!

V0303_08_00_37_0.text: I activate the Trap, Miracle Restoring!

V0303_08_00_38_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Magician Navigation!

V0303_08_00_39_0.text: I activate Magician Navigation's effect from my Graveyard!

V0303_09_00_00_0.text: Sentry Soldier of Stone's effect activates from my Grave!

V0303_09_00_01_0.text: Marshmacaron breaks apart into multiple pieces!

V0303_09_00_02_0.text: I send Clear Kuriboh to the Graveyard to negate the damage!

V0303_09_00_03_0.text: I banish Clear Kuriboh from the Graveyard to draw a card!

V0303_09_00_04_0.text: Since your monster has higher ATK, Gaia Lord powers up!

V0303_09_00_05_0.text: Yellow Gadget's effect adds Green Gadget to my hand!

V0303_09_00_06_0.text: Green Gadget's effect adds Red Gadget to my hand!

V0303_09_00_07_0.text: Red Gadget's effect adds Yellow Gadget to my hand!

V0303_09_00_08_0.text: Silver Gadget calls forth an ally!

V0303_09_00_09_0.text: When Silver Gadget is destroyed, it invites another Gadget!

V0303_09_00_10_0.text: Gold Gadget brings along a friend!

V0303_09_00_11_0.text: When Gold Gadget is destroyed, it calls out another Gadget!

V0303_09_00_12_0.text: I raise Silent Swordsman's Level this turn!

V0303_09_00_15_0.text: Silent Swordsman can stop a Spell Card from activating!

V0303_09_00_16_0.text: When Silent Swordsman falls, another takes its place!

V0303_09_00_18_0.text: Silent Magician negates the Spell Card's activation!

V0303_09_00_19_0.text: Even if Silent Magician is destroyed, its soul lives on!

V0303_09_00_20_0.text: Gandora's magical blast banishes all cards on the field!

V0303_09_00_22_0.text:
Witness Gandora's magical blast!
Boundless Gigarays!

V0303_09_00_25_0.text: Berry Magician Girl adds a Magician Girl to my hand!

V0303_09_00_26_0.text: Berry Magician Girl changes position to call a friend!

V0303_09_00_27_0.text: Lemon Magician Girl lets me add this card to my hand!

V0303_09_00_28_0.text: When Lemon Magician Girl is attacked, she'll use her effect!

V0303_09_00_29_0.text: When Apple Magician Girl is attacked, she summons a friend!

V0303_09_00_30_0.text: I get to add a Magician Girl in my Graveyard to my hand!

V0303_09_00_31_0.text: Chocolate Magician Girl's effect lets me draw a card!

V0303_09_00_32_0.text: When attacked, Chocolate Magician Girl uses her effect!

V0303_09_00_33_0.text: I activate Kiwi Magician Girl's effect from my hand!

V0303_09_00_34_0.text: Magician of Chaos's effect activates and destroys a card!

V0303_09_00_35_0.text: When it's destroyed, I can summon a Chaos Ritual Monster!

V0303_09_00_36_0.text: Magician of Black Chaos MAX's effect activates!

V0303_09_00_36_1.text: Your monsters can't activate their effects this turn!

V0303_09_00_37_0.text: Magician of Black Chaos MAX's effect now activates!

V0303_09_00_37_1.text: I add a Spell Card in my Graveyard to my hand!

V0303_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0303_13_00_00_0.text: Stand guard, Sentry Soldier of Stone!

V0303_13_00_03_0.text: Here comes Lord Gaia the Fierce Knight!

V0303_13_00_14_0.text:
That's right!
Silent Magician is now LV8!

V0303_13_00_16_0.text: I'll use this monster to defeat your deck!

V0303_13_00_16_1.text: Join me, Gandora the Dragon of Destruction!

V0303_13_00_17_0.text: Emerge, Gigarays Gandora the Dragon of Destruction!

V0303_37_00_00_0.text: Break free from your iron prison!

V0303_13_00_24_0.text: Join the Duel, Dark Magician Girl!

V0303_13_00_25_0.text: Bear witness to my ardent ally, Dark Magician!

V0303_13_00_27_0.text:
Descend!
Magician of Black Chaos MAX!

V0303_13_00_28_0.text:
This Trap Monster will defend my Field!
Metamorphortress!

V0303_13_00_29_0.text: My Trap Monster, Metalhold the Moving Blockade!

V0303_13_00_29_1.text: And it'll hold some metal to power itself up!

V0303_13_00_30_0.text:
My Trap Monster, Stronghold the Moving Fortress!
Get moving!

V0303_19_00_03_0.text:
Lord Gaia the Fierce Knight!
Spear 'em!

V0303_19_00_16_0.text: Gandora the Dragon of Destruction! Attack!

V0303_19_00_17_0.text: Blast 'em, Gigarays Gandora the Dragon of Destruction!

V0303_19_00_18_0.text: Attack, Gandora-X the Dragon of Demolition!

V0303_19_00_20_0.text:
Lemon Magician Girl!
Leave a sour taste in their mouth!

V0303_19_00_27_0.text: Magician of Black Chaos MAX! Attack!

V0303_28_00_01_0.text: I have a whole future ahead of me, so I'll never give up!

V0303_28_00_02_0.text: I made a promise to a friend.

V0303_28_00_02_1.text:
And it's one I intend to keep!
That's why I can't lose!

V0303_28_00_05_0.text: I know you want to resurrect the Pharaoh.

V0303_28_00_05_1.text: But you have to let him go.

V0303_28_00_07_0.text: I know you believe you're fighting for a noble cause.

V0303_28_00_07_1.text: But when you use hate to achieve peace, you’ve already lost.

V0303_28_00_08_0.text: No matter how dark things may get, I believe in my friends.

V0303_28_00_08_1.text: And we will create a bright future together!

V0303_29_00_01_0.text: I made a promise, but I couldn't keep it...

V0303_29_00_06_0.text: You have all the skills to become a pro Duelist, Joey!

V0303_29_00_07_0.text: You built a great deck, Téa!

V0303_33_00_01_0.text: I made a promise to a friend!

V0303_30_00_01_0.text: No one does that these days!

V0303_30_00_02_0.text: If you use hate to achieve peace, you've already lost.

V0303_34_00_00_0.text: I always put this card in my deck.

V0303_34_00_01_0.text: This is the moment I was waiting for!

V0303_34_00_05_0.text: I trapped you in a loop!

V0303_34_00_08_0.text: My monsters and I will defeat you together!

V0303_35_00_00_0.text:
He's...
He's no longer inside me...

V0303_35_00_01_0.text: I will do anything for a friend!
